---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Services" description="Digital strategy, UX design, visual design and AI-driven development from Whiteport.">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <header class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Our services</h1>
        <p class="text-wp-grey max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We combine strategic design thinking with modern AI technology to deliver digital solutions that make business sense.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-wp-blue/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-wp-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 18v-5.25m0 0a6.01 6.01 0 0 0 1.5-.189m-1.5.189a6.01 6.01 0 0 1-1.5-.189m3.75 7.478a12.06 12.06 0 0 1-4.5 0m3.75 2.383a14.406 14.406 0 0 1-3 0M14.25 18v-.192c0-.983.658-1.823 1.508-2.316a7.5 7.5 0 1 0-7.517 0c.85.493 1.509 1.333 1.509 2.316V18" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Digital strategy</h2>
          <p class="text-wp-grey leading-relaxed">
            Understanding your business, customers and their driving forces is the foundation of every digital project we take on. We help you define a clear digital strategy that aligns with your business goals and creates measurable results.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-wp-blue/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-wp-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.042 21.672 13.684 16.6m0 0-2.51 2.225.569-9.47 5.227 7.917-3.286-.672ZM12 2.25V4.5m5.834.166-1.591 1.591M20.25 10.5H18M7.757 14.743l-1.59 1.591M6 10.5H3.75m4.007-4.243-1.59-1.591" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">UX & Interaction design</h2>
          <p class="text-wp-grey leading-relaxed">
            We create comfortable and visually appealing interactions with users to minimize friction and maximize conversion in any digital system. From wireframes to prototypes to polished interfaces.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-wp-blue/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-wp-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.42 15.17 17.25 21A2.652 2.652 0 0 0 21 17.25l-5.877-5.877M11.42 15.17l2.496-3.03c.317-.384.74-.626 1.208-.766M11.42 15.17l-4.655 5.653a2.548 2.548 0 1 1-3.586-3.586l6.837-5.63m5.108-.233c.55-.164 1.163-.188 1.743-.14a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 4.486-6.336l-3.276 3.277a3.004 3.004 0 0 1-2.25-2.25l3.276-3.276a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-6.336 4.486c.091 1.076-.071 2.264-.904 2.95l-.102.085m-1.745 1.437L5.909 7.5H4.5L2.25 3.75l1.5-1.5L7.5 4.5v1.409l4.26 4.26m-1.745 1.437 1.745-1.437m6.615 8.206L15.75 15.75M4.867 19.125h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Requirement engineering</h2>
          <p class="text-wp-grey leading-relaxed">
            We make sure the system works as intended by careful logical analysis through the design and development process. Clear requirements lead to better products and fewer surprises.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-wp-blue/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-wp-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.53 16.122a3 3 0 0 0-5.78 1.128 2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.4 2.245 4.5 4.5 0 0 0 8.4-2.245c0-.399-.078-.78-.22-1.128Zm0 0a15.998 15.998 0 0 0 3.388-1.62m-5.043-.025a15.994 15.994 0 0 1 1.622-3.395m3.42 3.42a15.995 15.995 0 0 0 4.764-4.648l3.876-5.814a1.151 1.151 0 0 0-1.597-1.597L14.146 6.32a15.996 15.996 0 0 0-4.649 4.763m3.42 3.42a6.776 6.776 0 0 0-3.42-3.42" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Visual design</h2>
          <p class="text-wp-grey leading-relaxed">
            We carefully craft the visual experience and responsive design through an extensive attention to details and sober finishing touches. Every pixel matters.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-wp-blue/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-wp-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09ZM18.259 8.715 18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.456 2.456L21.75 6l-1.035.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.456 2.456ZM16.894 20.567 16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423 1.423Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">AI-Driven design & development</h2>
          <p class="text-wp-grey leading-relaxed">
            AI is opening new avenues of creation and has become our favorite tool to enable and speed up the design and development process. From AI agents to automated workflows.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-wp-blue/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-wp-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 6.75 22.5 12l-5.25 5.25m-10.5 0L1.5 12l5.25-5.25m7.5-3-4.5 16.5" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">System development</h2>
          <p class="text-wp-grey leading-relaxed">
            Through our vast network of development teams we can effectively create and improve a site or system built on any technology. From WordPress to React to Astro.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-16">
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@whiteport.com"
          class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-wp-cta text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-wp-cta-hover transition-colors no-underline"
        >
          Hire us for your projects!
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
